Author: GitHub
Title: Open Source Friday: E2B - a secure cloud environment for agents
Description:
This #OpenSourceFriday, we're spotlighting E2B, open source infrastructure runtime environment transforming how developers build AI-powered agents and autonomous applications. E2B makes it easier for developers to create, run, and manage sandboxed, long-running cloud processes for agents and AI-native apps. E2B is built to be secure, scalable, and developer-friendly, enabling new possibilities in LLM-powered products with “Cloud for AI Agents.”

Website: https://e2b.dev/ GitHub Repository: https://github.com/e2b-dev
